{{> nav}}
<main id="main-content" class="inner-page">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow reveal">About NA Dev Studio</div>
      <h1 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">A Lahore-Based Agency Building Products for the World</h1>
      <p class="section-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">We are a web development and mobile app studio helping startups and businesses turn ideas into fast, scalable digital products — from first prototype to production launch.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="page-stats reveal">
      <div class="page-stat">
        <span class="page-stat-num">50+</span>
        <span class="page-stat-label">Projects Delivered</span>
      </div>
      <div class="page-stat">
        <span class="page-stat-num">98%</span>
        <span class="page-stat-label">Client Satisfaction</span>
      </div>
      <div class="page-stat">
        <span class="page-stat-num">2–4 wks</span>
        <span class="page-stat-label">Average MVP Timeline</span>
      </div>
      <div class="page-stat">
        <span class="page-stat-num">24/7</span>
        <span class="page-stat-label">Support Available</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-split reveal">
      <div class="page-split-content">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>NA Dev Studio started with a simple belief: businesses in Pakistan and abroad deserve the same quality of software that Silicon Valley companies get — without Silicon Valley prices or timezone headaches.</p>
        <p>Based in Lahore, we work with founders, SMEs, and enterprise teams across Pakistan, the Middle East, Europe, and North America. Every project gets a dedicated designer, developer, and project lead working in sync — not a solo freelancer juggling five clients.</p>
        <p>We specialize in custom websites, e-commerce platforms, mobile apps, and full-stack web applications. Our stack is modern (React, Next.js, Node.js, PostgreSQL), our process is transparent, and our code is built to scale.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="page-split-visual">
        <img
          src="/images/why-dashboard.webp"
          alt="NA Dev Studio project dashboard with delivery metrics and client satisfaction scores"
          class="why-dashboard-img"
          loading="lazy"
          width="960"
          height="640"
          decoding="async"
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-block reveal">
      <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      <div class="why-features page-why-features">
        <div class="why-feat">
          <div class="why-feat-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Speed Without Shortcuts</h3>
            <p>Most MVPs ship in 2–4 weeks. We use agile sprints with daily updates so you see real progress, not vague promises.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-feat">
          <div class="why-feat-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Production-Ready Code</h3>
            <p>Clean architecture, documented APIs, and tested deployments. Your product is built to grow, not patched together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-feat">
          <div class="why-feat-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Dedicated Team</h3>
            <p>You work with a designer, developer, and PM — plus a private Slack or WhatsApp channel for direct communication.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-feat">
          <div class="why-feat-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Honest Pricing</h3>
            <p>Fixed-price scopes or transparent hourly retainers. No surprise invoices, no scope creep without your approval.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-block reveal">
      <h2>How We Work With Clients</h2>
      <p class="page-lead">Whether you are a first-time founder or an established business, our process stays the same: understand the problem, design the solution, build iteratively, and launch with confidence.</p>
      <div class="process-steps page-process">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <h3>Discovery</h3>
          <p>We learn your goals, users, and constraints in a focused kickoff call.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <h3>Design</h3>
          <p>Figma prototypes and wireframes before a single line of code is written.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <h3>Build</h3>
          <p>Weekly demos, live previews, and direct access to your project channel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">04</div>
          <h3>Launch</h3>
          <p>Deployment, handover docs, and optional ongoing maintenance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-block reveal">
      <h2>Who We Serve</h2>
      <div class="page-tags">
        <span class="service-tag">Startups &amp; MVPs</span>
        <span class="service-tag">E-Commerce Brands</span>
        <span class="service-tag">SaaS Companies</span>
        <span class="service-tag">Restaurants &amp; Retail</span>
        <span class="service-tag">Healthcare &amp; Fitness</span>
        <span class="service-tag">Agencies &amp; Enterprises</span>
      </div>
      <p class="page-lead">We serve clients in Lahore, across Pakistan, and internationally. Remote collaboration is our default — timezone-friendly updates and async communication that keeps projects moving.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="page-cta reveal">
      <h2>Ready to work with us?</h2>
      <p>Tell us about your project and we will reply within 24 hours with a clear plan — not just a price tag.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start Your Project</a>
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">View Our Work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
{{> footer}}
